00:22:32,839 --> 00:22:33,759
Lord Yuwen.

284
00:22:36,480 --> 00:22:37,079
Lord Grand Secretary.

285
00:22:37,319 --> 00:22:39,039
I already said my young master is not available to receive guests.

286
00:22:39,200 --> 00:22:40,000
Why are you forcing your way in?

287
00:22:42,759 --> 00:22:44,599
My lord, does this count as trespassing?

288
00:22:48,960 --> 00:22:49,960
The matter is urgent.

289
00:22:50,839 --> 00:22:51,559
I had no other choice.

290
00:22:57,440 --> 00:22:58,160
Go pour some tea.

291
00:22:59,519 --> 00:23:00,359
I'd like to see

292
00:23:01,079 --> 00:23:02,559
what urgent matter you have, my lord.

293
00:23:20,079 --> 00:23:20,559
Speak.

294
00:23:21,480 --> 00:23:22,960
Lord Yuwen has come to my Meng residence.

295
00:23:23,440 --> 00:23:24,359
For what purpose?

296
00:23:27,000 --> 00:23:29,400
Has Grand Preceptor Meng sent any letters home recently?

297
00:23:32,400 --> 00:23:32,920
What is it?

298
00:23:34,920 --> 00:23:35,920
It's nothing of great importance.

299
00:23:36,480 --> 00:23:38,599
I'm merely asking when the Grand Preceptor will return.

300
00:23:40,240 --> 00:23:42,559
My lord is quite concerned with my father's whereabouts.

301
00:23:44,440 --> 00:23:46,960
His Majesty is waiting for the Grand Preceptor to return to establish the Academy of Letters and Virtue.

302
00:23:47,720 --> 00:23:49,119
Lord Yuwen barges into my Meng residence.

303
00:23:50,440 --> 00:23:51,359
Is it just for this matter?

304
00:23:52,039 --> 00:23:55,039
The Academy of Letters and Virtue concerns the numerous students of Yunmi.

305
00:23:55,720 --> 00:23:56,599
Such an important matter.

306
00:23:57,000 --> 00:23:58,279
Naturally, I must be attentive to it.

307
00:24:00,559 --> 00:24:02,680
Lord Yuwen is truly dedicated to the state and its people.

308
00:24:03,920 --> 00:24:05,400
That is how an official should be.

309
00:24:07,799 --> 00:24:08,480
The tea has gone cold.

310
00:24:08,920 --> 00:24:10,319
Would my lord like more tea?

311
00:24:10,559 --> 00:24:11,039
That won't be necessary.

312
00:24:11,319 --> 00:24:12,160
I have urgent business to attend to.

313
00:24:12,160 --> 00:24:12,599
A Lan.

314
00:24:13,160 --> 00:24:13,759
See our guest out.

315
00:24:17,720 --> 00:24:18,119
Young Master Meng.

316
00:24:19,200 --> 00:24:21,240
Where did this dagger come from?

317
00:24:25,720 --> 00:24:26,920
A gift from someone I cherish.

318
00:24:28,000 --> 00:24:28,480
What's wrong?

319
00:24:31,880 --> 00:24:32,720
Nothing, nothing.

320
00:24:33,000 --> 00:24:34,720
It's fine, it's fine.

321
00:24:50,200 --> 00:24:50,640
My lord.

322
00:24:51,039 --> 00:24:52,480
At 6:45 p.m., I was busy looking for the map.

323
00:24:52,599 --> 00:24:53,759
That's why I forgot to go find you.

324
00:24:55,319 --> 00:24:56,079
Aside from this matter,

325
00:24:56,519 --> 00:24:58,319
does the Fifth Princess have nothing else to say to me?

326
00:24:59,240 --> 00:24:59,640
Oh, right.

327
00:24:59,960 --> 00:25:02,000
Meng Shaojue has probably already realized I'm pretending to be foolish.

328
00:25:02,240 --> 00:25:03,039
But don't worry, my lord.

329
00:25:03,160 --> 00:25:04,160
He hasn't exposed me.

330
00:25:04,279 --> 00:25:05,400
So I'll keep pretending.

331
00:25:05,559 --> 00:25:07,039
Until I find the treasure map for you.

332
00:25:08,880 --> 00:25:10,839
That dagger was you who gave it to Meng Shaojue.

333
00:25:12,079 --> 00:25:13,279
You could say so.

334
00:25:15,200 --> 00:25:16,559
If I'm not mistaken,

335
00:25:16,960 --> 00:25:18,640
it's exactly the one I won at the auction.

336
00:25:19,839 --> 00:25:21,200
Didn't you not want it anymore, my lord?

337
00:25:21,400 --> 00:25:22,160
So it conveniently fell into my hands.

338
00:25:22,640 --> 00:25:23,880
And then you gave it to Meng Shaojue.

339
00:25:30,160 --> 00:25:30,759
Fifth Princess.

340
00:25:32,079 --> 00:25:33,519
Our engagement has not yet been canceled.

341
00:25:34,119 --> 00:25:35,160
In name,

342
00:25:35,640 --> 00:25:37,160
you are still my betrothed.

343
00:25:38,640 --> 00:25:39,359
Rest assured, my lord.

344
00:25:39,599 --> 00:25:40,400
Once I return to the palace,

345
00:25:40,400 --> 00:25:42,480
I'll immediately find a way to cancel our engagement.

346
00:25:48,559 --> 00:25:49,400
I told you to find the map.

347
00:25:49,400 --> 00:25:50,720
I didn't tell you to use any honey trap.

348
00:25:51,640 --> 00:25:52,799
Honey trap?

349
00:25:54,000 --> 00:25:54,440
My lord.

350
00:25:54,759 --> 00:25:55,640
Are you saying...

351
00:25:55,640 --> 00:25:56,640
that I also count as a beauty?

352
00:25:58,920 --> 00:25:59,960
I'm kindly reminding you.

353
00:26:01,079 --> 00:26:02,799
Don't do anything that damages my reputation.

354
00:26:04,240 --> 00:26:05,240
Otherwise, what you'll have to worry about

355
00:26:05,680 --> 00:26:07,240
won't just be Xiao Lizi.

356
00:26:24,039 --> 00:26:24,440
My lord.

357
00:26:24,920 --> 00:26:25,799
Why did Young Master Meng say

358
00:26:25,799 --> 00:26:27,319
that dagger was a gift from someone he cherishes?

359
00:26:29,799 --> 00:26:30,519
Your servant understands.

360
00:26:31,240 --> 00:26:32,480
After the Fifth Princess picked up the dagger,

361
00:26:32,480 --> 00:26:33,440
she gave it to Young Master Meng.

362
00:26:33,839 --> 00:26:35,599
She must have fallen for Young Master Meng.

363
00:26:35,920 --> 00:26:37,519
And Young Master Meng also has feelings for the Fifth Princess.

364
00:26:39,039 --> 00:26:41,640
No wonder the Fifth Princess sneaked into the Meng residence.

365
00:26:42,039 --> 00:26:43,039
So that's how it is.

366
00:26:43,759 --> 00:26:44,440
I dare bet

367
00:26:44,799 --> 00:26:46,640
she must have had her eye on Young Master Meng for a long time.

368
00:26:48,640 --> 00:26:49,160
Bet what?

369
00:26:49,440 --> 00:26:49,920
Bet what?

370
00:26:50,640 --> 00:26:51,640
If your servant loses the bet,

371
00:26:51,759 --> 00:26:52,599
according to Shadow Guard rules,

372
00:26:52,960 --> 00:26:53,799
I'll wear women's clothing

373
00:26:53,799 --> 00:26:55,160
and spar with everyone in the residence.

374
00:26:57,480 --> 00:26:59,480
Since when did the Shadow Guard have such a rule?

375
00:27:02,359 --> 00:27:02,799
Yes.

376
00:27:12,960 --> 00:27:14,079
What are you standing around for?

377
00:27:17,200 --> 00:27:18,039
Grind the ink.

378
00:27:26,880 --> 00:27:29,359
Meng Shaojue wouldn't keep the key on his person, would he?

379
00:27:34,880 --> 00:27:35,279
A Lan.

380
00:27:39,880 --> 00:27:40,279
A Lan.

381
00:27:41,799 --> 00:27:42,319
Young master.

382
00:27:44,319 --> 00:27:46,039
What did I just say?

383
00:27:56,000 --> 00:27:57,680
In a few days, it will be my birthday.

384
00:27:59,319 --> 00:27:59,920
A Lan.

385
00:28:01,640 --> 00:28:02,680
What are you planning to give me?

386
00:28:03,799 --> 00:28:05,119
This servant has no money.

387
00:28:15,200 --> 00:28:16,160
Could it be in his belt?

388
00:28:18,599 --> 00:28:19,160
Young master!

389
00:28:19,559 --> 00:28:20,720
You're harassing this servant!

390
00:28:25,519 --> 00:28:26,960
You're the one harassing me.

391
00:28:27,519 --> 00:28:28,480
This servant wouldn't dare.

392
00:28:31,720 --> 00:28:32,759
You still say you wouldn't dare?

393
00:28:36,759 --> 00:28:37,440
It's dirty.

394
00:28:52,599 --> 00:28:53,000
It's smudged.

395
00:29:02,519 --> 00:29:03,039
Someone!

396
00:29:03,640 --> 00:29:04,200
Prepare water.

397
00:29:21,880 --> 00:29:22,440
Come here.

398
00:29:27,400 --> 00:29:28,039
Young master.

399
00:29:28,440 --> 00:29:29,759
The storybooks say

400
00:29:29,920 --> 00:29:32,599
men and women must keep their distance.

401
00:29:34,880 --> 00:29:36,240
The storybooks also have

402
00:29:36,640 --> 00:29:39,319
stories of maids and young masters living happily ever after.

403
00:29:40,079 --> 00:29:40,640
Haven't you heard?

404
00:29:45,599 --> 00:29:46,519
Hurry up and come here.

405
00:29:59,079 --> 00:30:00,200
You just wait.

406
00:30:08,920 --> 00:30:09,839
A fool.

407
00:30:10,759 --> 00:30:11,559
can also be shy.

408
00:30:14,240 --> 00:30:15,160
Young master.

409
00:30:16,200 --> 00:30:17,640
This servant thinks...

410
00:30:20,319 --> 00:30:21,440
This servant thinks...

411
00:30:22,519 --> 00:30:25,079
Young master's skin is so fair.

412
00:30:30,640 --> 00:30:32,279
It smells nice too.

413
00:30:33,240 --> 00:30:34,640
I wonder if it feels...

414
00:30:35,119 --> 00:30:37,279
smoother than an egg.

415
00:30:39,440 --> 00:30:40,079
Young master.

416
00:30:40,359 --> 00:30:41,279
Can this servant touch...

417
00:30:41,720 --> 00:30:42,160
Wait a moment.

418
00:30:45,759 --> 00:30:48,480
Then, should we wipe your chest?

419
00:30:48,480 --> 00:30:49,400
You... you should leave.

420
00:30:54,039 --> 00:30:54,759
Alright.

421
00:31:06,160 --> 00:31:06,920
Young master.

422
00:31:07,039 --> 00:31:08,559
This servant will come back later.

423
00:31:15,240 --> 00:31:16,400
Don't forget the birthday gift.

424
00:31:17,400 --> 00:31:18,839
Understood, young master.

425
00:31:58,000 --> 00:31:58,880
Xiao Hei.

426
00:32:01,000 --> 00:32:01,519
Xiao Hei.

427
00:32:03,279 --> 00:32:03,799
Xiao Hei.

428
00:33:23,920 --> 00:33:24,519
Eldest Cousin.

429
00:33:25,359 --> 00:33:26,359
How has A Lan been recently?

430
00:33:29,440 --> 00:33:30,079
The Miracle Doctor said

431
00:33:30,680 --> 00:33:31,640
she can be visited in two days.

432
00:33:33,759 --> 00:33:34,400
Don't worry, A Zi.

433
00:33:34,680 --> 00:33:35,640
A Lan will be fine.

434
00:33:37,680 --> 00:33:39,200
Then I'll go to your villa the day after tomorrow to see her.

435
00:33:40,279 --> 00:33:40,839
The day after tomorrow won't work.

436
00:33:41,480 --> 00:33:42,960
The day after tomorrow is Meng Shaojue's birthday.

437
00:33:43,200 --> 00:33:44,720
Eldest Brother is going with me.

438
00:33:46,559 --> 00:33:47,480
Eldest Cousin is also going.

439
00:33:49,240 --> 00:33:49,599
Eldest Brother.

440
00:33:50,480 --> 00:33:53,079
Shao Jue is actually a gentleman worth befriending.

441
00:33:53,079 --> 00:33:54,799
You'll know once you spend more time with him.

442
00:33:56,960 --> 00:33:58,039
I have something to attend to, I must go.

443
00:34:07,200 --> 00:34:09,519
Eldest Cousin and Young Master Meng have never gotten along.

444
00:34:10,320 --> 00:34:11,840
Why do you want to go to his birthday banquet?

445
00:34:16,199 --> 00:34:17,920
Last time I went to the Meng residence with Eldest Cousin,

446
00:34:18,599 --> 00:34:19,880
I thought he was acting a bit strange.

447
00:34:24,440 --> 00:34:24,880
I see.

448
00:34:25,519 --> 00:34:27,000
The day after tomorrow, I'll go to the Meng residence with you.

449
00:34:34,639 --> 00:34:35,039
My lord.

450
00:34:35,440 --> 00:34:36,360
The fake map has been swapped.

451
00:34:44,239 --> 00:34:44,639
My lord.

452
00:34:44,960 --> 00:34:45,679
We have an agreement.

453
00:34:45,920 --> 00:34:48,119
Xiao Lizi, you must not touch him again.

454
00:34:51,559 --> 00:34:52,239
Do you really think

455
00:34:54,199 --> 00:34:55,199
I would kill Xiao Lizi?

456
00:35:04,119 --> 00:35:04,519
Your Majesty

457
00:35:04,519 --> 00:35:05,599
has covered for you long enough.

458
00:35:06,599 --> 00:35:07,599
It's time for you to leave the Meng residence.

459
00:35:08,480 --> 00:35:10,119
When the time comes, I will return naturally.

460
00:35:11,360 --> 00:35:11,800
My lord.

461
00:35:12,360 --> 00:35:13,639
The map has now been swapped.

462
00:35:14,119 --> 00:35:15,880
What do you plan to do next?

463
00:35:18,800 --> 00:35:20,440
Knowing too much is not good for you.

464
00:35:21,039 --> 00:35:22,639
I already know more than enough.

465
00:35:23,039 --> 00:35:23,719
One more thing won't make a difference.

466
00:35:24,239 --> 00:35:25,239
The fake map has been poisoned.

467
00:35:25,800 --> 00:35:27,719
The day after tomorrow, just let Prince Ning's men steal it.

468
00:35:29,960 --> 00:35:30,679
Then I... I...

469
00:35:31,000 --> 00:35:31,639
Don't worry.

470
00:35:32,719 --> 00:35:33,760
Your poison was just neutralized.

471
00:35:41,440 --> 00:35:42,280
Then, my lord,

472
00:35:42,840 --> 00:35:44,840
the day after tomorrow is Meng Shaojue's birthday.

473
00:35:45,440 --> 00:35:46,199
I'm worried

474
00:35:46,199 --> 00:35:47,320
Young Master Meng is highly skilled in martial arts.

475
00:35:47,960 --> 00:35:49,199
That's not for you to worry about.

476
00:35:50,400 --> 00:35:51,880
My concern is for Miss Meng Yinglu.

477
00:35:52,800 --> 00:35:53,280
My lord,

478
00:35:54,239 --> 00:35:55,119
could you

479
00:35:55,639 --> 00:35:56,679
send someone to protect her?

480
00:35:58,679 --> 00:35:59,639
Commander He will also be going.

481
00:36:00,159 --> 00:36:01,320
I've put him in charge of this matter.

482
00:36:04,079 --> 00:36:04,800
If there's nothing else,

483
00:36:04,960 --> 00:36:05,639
I'll take my leave now.

484
00:36:06,239 --> 00:36:07,719
I lied to Meng Shaojue, saying

485
00:36:07,760 --> 00:36:09,480
I went out to buy him a birthday gift.

486
00:36:09,800 --> 00:36:10,639
I need to go buy something quickly.

487
00:36:11,039 --> 00:36:11,679
That dagger

488
00:36:13,440 --> 00:36:14,119
is worth ten thousand taels.

489
00:36:18,119 --> 00:36:18,599
My lord.

490
00:36:19,079 --> 00:36:21,199
That dagger was the last birthday gift

491
00:36:21,320 --> 00:36:23,719
his mother gave him before she passed.

492
00:36:24,880 --> 00:36:26,599
It was a gift from Meng Shaojue's mother.

493
00:36:31,519 --> 00:36:32,440
You were the one who found the dagger.

494
00:36:32,960 --> 00:36:33,679
You can take it.

495
00:36:34,199 --> 00:36:34,760
Thank you, my lord.

496
00:36:35,000 --> 00:36:35,400
However,

497
00:36:36,920 --> 00:36:37,760
one thing for another.

498
00:36:38,440 --> 00:36:39,400
What will you give me in return?
